<br />

<br />
At 55 you can start putting AA points into Mental Clarity but it's expensive and time consuming at that level... first 2 AA levels buys you 1mana/tick.. then it costs 4 more to get 2 mana/tick.. 6 AA's just for 2 mana/tick...lol.. of course for a bard that extra one or two mana is very noticable.  I do a lot of chant kiting and doubling and trippleing my mana regen greatly speeds up the process.</span></td>
